Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,0)}影像互相重疊 My Heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(0,160)}breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,160)}擦身而過就像風一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,120)}無法抓住 Why it is you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,0)}無法到達的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(0,160)}一個人獨自痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,0)}不一樣的言語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}在夜空下 和星星一起流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(200,0)}不再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}Ah 就算悲傷 也只是剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}是與你一起出生的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}{\fad(160,0)}Ah 就這樣漂浮著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000093&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord2}在心裏的屋裏面
